NEWS GOV-MO: University of Macau awarded the degree of honorary doctorate to 7 distinguished people The “Award-giving Ceremony for Honorary Degree and Higher Degree” was held in University of Macau today (the 11th day of this month), to award the degree of honorary doctorate of Australia to Liu Zunyi, Chen Kaixian, Shuji Nakamura, Li Lanjuan, Li Xiaoliang, Zhu Lilan and Jiang Zhaohui, to commend their excellent achievements and their great contributions made to social and educational development. At the award-giving ceremony, Ouyang Yu, the chief executive, the representative of the university superintendent of University of Macau and the director of the Social Culture Department, awarded the degree of honorary doctorate with the accompanying of Lin Jincheng, the chairman of the university board, and Song Yonghua, the president of University of Macau. Professor Liu Zunyi was awarded with the honorary degree of Doctor of Education; Professor Chen Kaixian was awarded with the honorary degree of Doctor of Science; Professor Shuji Nakamura was awarded with the honorary degree of Doctor of Science; Professor Li Lanjuan was awarded with the honorary degree of Doctor of Science; Professor Li Xiaoliang was awarded with the honorary degree of Doctor of Business Administration; Professor Zhu Lilan was awarded with the honorary degree of Doctor of Science and Ms. Jiang Zhaohui was awarded with the honorary degree of Doctor of Science. In his speech, firstly, Ouyang Yu showed enthusiastic congratulations and great respect to the seven distinguished people awarded with the honorary doctorate, who made excellent achievements in different fields and made excellent contributions to the development of the country and the progress of the world; at the same time, Ouyang Yu showed the most sincere wishes to the graduates and their parents, and showed sincere respect to the teachers who cherished their posts and were devoted to it, with exquisite academic skills. When reading out the praise to Liu Zunyi, Sun Yifeng, a chair professor of the Faculty of Humanities of University of Macau, praised Professor Liu Zunyi as an economist famous all over the whole world, who is famous for his excellent academic achievements and prospective education ideas. In addition to the achievements made in economic development, economic growth and economy in East Asia, he is also a prospective leader in education. In brief, he has excellent achievements in many fields. When reading out the praise to Shuji Nakamura, Sun Yifeng expressed that Professor Shuji Nakamura is a pioneer in the sustainable energy technology field. He is one of the three prize winners of 2014 Nobel Prize in Physics with his invention of blue LED. The invention of Professor Shuji Nakamura has thoroughly changed the lighting industry and has promoted the generation of the white LED widely applied to daily life and industrial production today, making great contributions to welfare of human beings. When reading out the praise to Li Lanjuan, Sun Yifeng praised her as the pioneer of the artificial liver industry in China, who has created the unique and effective Li’s artificial liver system, with great breakthroughs in treatment of severe hepatitis and hepatic failure, significantly reducing the fatality rate of hepatic failure. In the fight against the COVID-19, the “four-against and two-balance” scheme proposed by her and her team and the three technologies including artificial liver, micro-ecology and stem cells significantly improved the treat and cure rate of severe cases. When reading out the praise to Li Xiaoliang, Sun Yifeng praised him to lay a foundation for creative research on operation management, establishing the idea method for the theory and practice of supply chain and thoroughly changing the commercial mode all over the whole world. Famous for popularizing the conception of bullwhip effect in operation management, Li Xiaoliang has explored the measures to cope with this phenomenon. Today, in the epidemic and the intense situations in economics all over the whole world, the bullwhip effect has been increasingly prominent, leading to serious destruction in the supply chain. The prospective research conducted by Li Xiaoliang is just as fuel in snowy weather, helping related industries to cope with difficulties, so as to bring in huge social values. When reading out the praise to Li Zhu Lilan, Sun Yifeng expressed that Zhu Lilan found a breakthrough and creative staining technique during scientific research works for preparing samples, enjoying great popularity in science and technology at home and abroad. She was awarded with honorary titles such as an academician of International Eurasian Academy of Sciences with her excellent scientific achievements, to win the lofty position in the Temple of science and technology all over the whole world within her splendid performance. When reading out the praise of Chen Kaixian, Chen Xin, the acting dean of Institute of China Medical Study of University of Macau, expressed, Professor Chen Kaixin has been engaged in research and development of drugs for more than 40 years, who has owned lofty international status and reputation due to his excellent scientific achievements as well as his great contributions made to the country, Macau, University of Macau and national key laboratories. His active driving actions to the development of Traditional Chinese Medicine to Macau and the Guangdong-Hong Kong-Macau Greater Bay Area has sufficiently reflected his sense of mission in contribution to medical development strategy in our country. When reading out the praise of Jiang Zhaohui, Xu Chengzhong, dean of the Institute of Technology of University of Macau, expressed that 15 significant inventions and patients invented with the participation of Ms. Jiang Zhaohui are related to storage virtualization, navigation, document system and power management, which are all widely applied with favorable practice, improving the convenience of life. As an inventor with excellent achievements, Ms. Jiang can change advanced science, technology and theory into simple ones, to popularize it to the public. Finally, Chen Kaixian read out the acknowledgement as the representative of the honorary doctorates. He was very glad that the medicine industry of Macau and the Guangdong-Hong Kong-Macau Greater Bay Area set a good demonstration: from the first State Key Laboratory of Traditional Chinese Medicine Quality Research established by University of Macau to flourishing development of Traditional Chinese Medicine of the Guangdong-Hong Kong-Macau Greater Bay Area, University of Macau has played huge roles in integrating excellent talents of the medicine industry of Macau and the Guangdong-Hong Kong-Macau Greater Bay Area. In addition, he considered that the management team of University of Macau was prospective, who not only provided soils for scientific research for students but also provided the society with talents with sense of responsibility. He was honored to develop exchange and cooperation with University of Macau, and showed sincere congratulations to the achievements made by University of Macau in recent years.
